 <H1>PROPPATCH Method - Motivation</H1> 
 <P><UL>
<LI><H2>A mechanism is needed to create properties
</H2>
<UL>
<LI>As PUT isnï¿½t really suitable for creating properties, a mechanism is still needed to create properties.
</UL></UL><UL>
<LI><H2>Atomicity
</H2>
<UL>
<LI>Most property scenarios require a way to atomically create and delete a number of properties in order to keep the resource in a consistent state.</UL></UL></P>
